#!/bin/bash
gen a4 15 'A dark-haired girl meditates cross-legged on the laboratory floor, palms open, a faint violet shimmer about her; behind her, inside the glowing amber tank, the small pale creature drifts gently near the glass, watching her. The monitor trace quickens, then settles; the creature slowly uncurls. The camera holds steady throughout. The scene is quiet, with only soft ambient sound. Everyone remains as they appear in the opening frame.' --start-image mewtwo/frames2/a4.png --image mewtwo/anchors/sabrina_teen.png --image mewtwo/anchors/mewtwo_pod.png
gen a6 10 'The young creature presses close to the pod glass, staring at itself in the wheeled mirror; its reflection stares back through amber fluid. It slowly lifts its gaze from the mirror. Staff in the background keep their faces turned away. The camera holds steady throughout. The scene is quiet, with only soft ambient sound. Everyone remains as they appear in the opening frame.' --start-image mewtwo/frames2/a6.png --image mewtwo/anchors/mewtwo_pod.png --image mewtwo/anchors/sabrina_teen.png
gen a7 15 'The man in the black suit stands before the glowing amber tank, hands clasped behind his back, golden light rimming his silhouette; inside, the slender pale shape drifts down through the glow toward him, and one small fist rests against the inner glass, then opens flat. The camera holds steady throughout. The scene is quiet, with only soft ambient sound. Everyone remains as they appear in the opening frame.' --start-image mewtwo/frames2/a7.png --image mewtwo/anchors/giovanni.png --image mewtwo/anchors/mewtwo_pod.png
